parameters:
\TA[1]What? Why the serious face all of a sudden? Did something
happen?
\TA[1]W-What are you talking about? A magical girl? Me?
\TA[1]Um, umm, isn't it a bit strict in terms of age?

\TA[1]I set myself as the first subscriber for Senpai's
livestream.
\TA[1]I already told you to end the livestream.

\TA[1]Anyway, you understand now, right? Whether Senpai's true
identity is exposed or not is in my hands.

\TA[1]When a magical girl's true identity becomes widely known,
they lose their power.

\TA[1]Hehe. If the villains I've defeated until now were to come
for revenge, it would be quite troublesome, wouldn't it,
Senpai?
\TA[1](Even though it's not well known, I know it accurately.)

\TA[1]...Even if I have to bear the penalty, I won't erase my
memories when the time comes...

\TA[1]You have a scary expression, Senpai. Hehe. Are you really
that afraid of your true identity being exposed?
\TA[1]Don't worry, Senpai. My desire is for you...

\TA[1]Don't you know? It's Robin from Batman, Watson from Holmes,
and Chiyose from Cardcaptor!

\TA[1]Well, I do know... but why did you become a sidekick
again?

\TA[1]Because it's exciting, isn't it! The only one who
understands the hidden magical girl's true identity!
\TA[1]I've always wanted to try it at least once.
\TA[1]I understand how you feel, but it's not allowed.

\TA[1]If you make one wrong move, there is a danger that you could
get injured or even die. There is also a possibility of
being taken hostage.

\TA[1]Of course, I'll handle things like that on my own. I'll also
do my job as a sidekick.

\TA[1]Please look. This is the location where missing persons
have been reported in the city over the past month.
\TA[1]...! Where did you get something like that...?

\TA[1]By the way, it seems like you're misunderstanding
something.

\TA[1]I'm not asking, I'm threatening you, you know? Are you okay
with your true identity being exposed, senpai?

\TA[1](No... no matter how capable this child is) (We can't
involve ordinary people.)
\TA[1](I have to refuse even if it's impossible--)

\TA[1]Hey! Don't come out on your own! If you get involved, the
situation will become complicated, you know!
\TA[1]Is this shitty cat your assigned mascot, senpai?

\TA[1]Kei, you're too clumsy. It's better to have at least one
person who knows the situation.

\TA[1](That's true... but) (Even though we might repeat the same
mistake again.)
\TA[1]Instead, you absolutely must not come to the battlefield.
\TA[1]Alright! Please take care of me from now on, senpai!

\TA[1]I understand, so please don't stick to me... It's
embarrassing...
